  "text": "One problem with these approaches is that they only scale to support as many remote participants as can be reasonably displayed on a screen of fixed size, and even this may tax instructors' perceptual capabilities. Full fidelity awareness also raises issues of privacy [CITATION_1] : the remote person is not in the classroom, and connecting the classroom to that person's physical space can introduce many problems.",
